 thi\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4194\" src=\"https:\/\/dienlanhhoangduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/250_259_tu_lanh_hitachi_r_wx74j_xh_00_wb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dienlanhhoangduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/250_259_tu_lanh_hitachi_r_wx74j_xh_00_wb.jpg 500w, https:\/\/dienlanhhoangduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/250_259_tu_lanh_hitachi_r_wx74j_xh_00_wb-45x45.jpg 45w, https:\/\/dienlanhhoangduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/250_259_tu_lanh_hitachi_r_wx74j_xh_00_wb-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><b><strong>C\u00e1c l\u1ed7i th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u1edf t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt<\/strong><\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i \u0111\u00e1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt m\u1ea5t l\u1ea1nh ng\u0103n d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0m \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 115%;\">T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba Nh\u1eadt b\u1ecb ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/